<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ferdinand" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ferdinand,</orth> 1) F. the Catholic, king of Spain: <bibl n="shak. h8 2.4.47" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 4, 47</bibl>. 2) the son of King Alonso of Naples: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.212" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 212</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.244" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 244</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.139.8" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 139</bibl>. 3) a cousin of Petruchio's: <bibl n="shak. shr 4.1.154" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 1, 154</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>